\pard\pardeftab720\sl260

\f0\fs26 \cf0 The guard station is here more to prevent light fingered goblins sneaking into Horse Gutters living area and store rooms than prevent a determined group. If a party appear without masking their approach the goblin bully Sloba Kneeeater will flee towards the Awaiting chamber (area 6) after commanding the young, brave and stupid runts to stop them. Sloba knows about the pit trap at 5. and will avoid it.
